      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/10/25750596/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_7805969031549199885.png",
                "id": "talent39819",
                "key": "Kamisato Art: Marobashi",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Kamisato Art: Marobashi"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>. Karakter ini memperoleh status <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Takimeguri Kanka</span>.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Takimeguri Kanka</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Normal Attack</span> Karakter yang terpengaruh mengakibatkan DMG +1 dan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> yang diakibatkan diubah menjadi<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> Hydro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 3</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/12/25750596/c9a590519c61a04cdf9f4ffe0789e577_2218097087008992977.png",
                "id": "talent98045",
                "key": "Kamisato Art: Kyouka",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Kamisato Art: Kyouka"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span> dan memanggil <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Garden of Purity</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/12/25750596/dbaf88377dd5ea97d834b2b4fe039f69_6986353709412900877.png",
                "id": "talent99707",
                "key": "Kamisato Art: Suiyuu",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Kamisato Art: Suiyuu"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Sel</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">esai:</span> Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 2</span><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat berada dalam </span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">arena:</span> Normal Attack Karakter milikmu mengakibatkan DMG +1.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/10/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6910978839126919143.png",
                "id": "talent73973",
                "key": "Garden of Purity",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/12/25750596/ad5eb2ee48365d340272b333689f3ebb_4746128377888056107.png",
                "title": "Garden of Purity"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Hydro dan memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, target tidak dapat melangkah di Ronde ini (Dapat dihapus di muka setelah target menerima Physical DMG atau Pyro DMG, namun DMG +2)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan sebuah [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] yang memberikan +2 poin DMG untuk kasus Pyro/Electro DMG-mu selanjutnya</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/10/25750596/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_7927245798509741883.png",
                "id": "talent19814",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/10/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_6654959951845287750.png",
                "id": "talent73526",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
